title: Jack Van Impe - Armageddon's 4 horsemen Mounting (VIDEO)
description:
"and I looked and behold a pale horse: and his name that sat on him was Death and Hell followed with him..." - Revelation 6:8

Death and Hell about to be unleashed on our world? Revelation 6 gives a horrifying description of the "four horsemen of the apocalypse" - and now Drs. Jack and Rexella Van Impe show you that those riders could be mounting their devastating steeds right now!

This video teaches using Bible prophecy and today's headlines to show you the startling truth - and help you answer critical questions such as:

-Who are the four horsemen?

-What does former Pope Benedict's conflict with Islamist reveal?

-What prophecy says Francis will be the last pope before the Anti-christ arises?

-What stands in the way of a one-world religion?

-What did Martin Luther King prophesy about Israel?

-When will there be peace in the Middle East?

-What role does Russia play in Armageddon?

-Has the horsemen of terrorism already been unleashed?

-Could Sharia law come to the USA?

-And many more
